Interface ObjectExpirationResult

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    CompleteMultipartUploadResult, CopyObjectResult, ObjectMetadata, PutObjectResult

    public interface ObjectExpirationResult
    Interface for service responses that receive the x-amz-expiration header.
    See Also:
    Headers.EXPIRATION
